## Paired Samples t-Test

### Compare Scores

1.  Calculate the difference between pre-mindfullness stress and post-mindfullness scores.




::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data_new <- 
  data |> 
  group_by(group) |> 
  mutate(
    id = paste0("Participant ",row_number()),
    group = ifelse(stringr::str_detect(group,"One"),"T1","T2")) |> 
  tidyr::pivot_wider(
                     names_from = group,
                     values_from = score
                     ) |> 
  ungroup() |> 
  mutate(
    D = T2-T1,
    Dfi = ifelse(stringr::str_detect(D,"^-"),paste0("(",D,")"),D)
  )

data_new |> 
  select(-D) |> 
  gt_preview() |> 
  opt_row_striping() |> 
    tab_options(
    table.font.size = 32,
    table.width = pct(70)
    ) |> 
    tab_style(
    style = cell_text(weight = "bold"),
    locations = cells_column_labels()
  )
```

